title: Saving Private Masko
description: Masko takes Axel's call for more discipline too seriously and loses sight of his own identity in the process, becoming a no-nonsense soldier set on toeing the line - and ill-equipped for a lucha libre with Madcap!

title: Bring Out Your Beast
description: Craig wants to play a popular card game, so he decides to borrow Bernard's vintage and valuable cards.

title: To Air Is Robot
description: Air Man stakes a claim on the skies above Silicon City, threatening anything that trespasses on his airspace.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Little Mer-Tiger
description: The origin of Tiger is told as a flashback.  As the legend goes, Tiger used to be a mermaid.  One day the evil ruler of the sea, Bubble Grandpa, demanded a hamburger and picked Tiger to retrieve it.  He used his magic sea powers to give Tiger legs and send her ashore.  But Tiger grew to love the land, and with the help of her new friend, Uncle Grandpa, defeated the evil sea ruler and got to keep her legs.

title: My Clique
description: Chloe, a child prodigy, finds it difficult to connect with her much older classmates. The Bears take her under their wing and show her how to make great college friends.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: Watt's Happening?!
description: When Elec Man derails the school play by hijacking Silicon Central's power, Aki/Mega Man must use what he has learned onstage to defeat his supercharged foe.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: Flyaway
description: When Adorabat's spirit transcends her body during a meditation exercise, Mao Mao and Badgerclops have to figure out a way to return her to the real world.

title: Steven Universe Future - Catch Up Trailer
description: Catch up on everything going on with Steven and the gems in Steven Universe Future so far!  This trailer covers the most important events of the first ten episodes of Steven Universe Future.

title: Game Show
description: While shopping with his Mom, Clarence discovers Breehn hiding in a clothes rack. Under the guise of trying on new clothes for their moms, they sneak out to find a local gameshow being hosted inside the Aberdale Mall.

title: Ramen
description: Los Osos bebé ayudan a una chef en apuros a perfeccionar su sopa de fideos y salvar su tienda.

title: Cartoon Feud
description: Control Freak forces the Titans and the Scooby Gang to compete on Family Feud.

title: Fire Maker
description: The Ice Emperor learns of the ninja's arrival and sends his Blizzard Samurai warriors to destroy them and the villagers who sheltered them.

title: The Curse
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP run afoul of some no-good teenage witches and are cursed! Lousy teenagers!

title: Elements Part 4: Cloudy
description: Before they can restore Ooo, Finn and Jake will have to escape exile in an endless sky.

title: Case Clothed
description: Princess Zange hires the Warriors to be her secret service for the afternoon to go shopping, but the looting pirates of Keelhaul Cove make fashion makeovers nearly impossible to manage.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star Part 1
description: The Justice League holds a talent competition to find a superhero worthy of joining the team.

title: Ghost Princess
description: Finn and Jake try to solve Ghost Princess' unsolved murder.

title: Dog Decider
description: Unable to make tough decisions, Craig decides to put his choices in the hands of a dog named Fred.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Tiger Fail
description: Gwen refuses to be pressured into choosing an ice cream flavor that she does not want.

title: Having the Timeout of Our Lives
description: Owen forms a special bond with Duncan after having loads of fun with him during their timeouts.

title: Crece
description: Mientras todo el mundo celebra a Valentino porque le creció su primer vello facial, Vic se pone celoso y recurre a métodos mágicos para dejarse crecer el bigote y competir por la atención.

title: Pleito animado
description: Control Fenómeno obliga a los Titanes y a la Scooby-pandilla a competir en Pleito Familiar.

title: Trials Part 1
description: Following the network of GroundBridges left by the Allspark, Optimus and Megatron finally discover the Allspark, and its Guardian, Cheetor.

title: Once Upon a Townsville
description: When a dainty princess on a mission comes to Townsville, the girls must learn the superhero way isn't always the right way.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: El Hacedor de Fuego
description: El Emperador de Hielo se entera de la llegada de los ninjas y envía a sus guerreros Samurais Blizzard a destruirlos, y a todos los aldeanos que los albergaron.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ghost Fly
description: Jake and the tree house are haunted by a vengeful spectre.

title: Proximo Idolo de la Liga de la Justicia: Parte 2
description: La competencia se enciende cuando Robin hace lo imposible por ganar.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 1
description: A dangerous lone gunslinger named WildWheel returns to Cybertron looking for Optimus Prime.

title: Bubblevision/Bought and Scold
description: Bubblevision: Bubbles' fighting has been really terribly lately and the Professor discovers she needs glasses. Bubbles is humiliated by these huge, horrible things and never wants to see or be seen again./Bough and Scold: When Princess buys Townsville, she makes crime legal. Now, the girls have nothing to do and the town is in shambles.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 2
description: After Victor loses a wrestling match, Victor and Valentino journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The Bakugan Battle League/The Ancient Elder
description: The Bakugan Battle League: Benton Dusk is in the process of renovating a state of the art Bakugan Brawling stadium. When it comes to brawling, who better to test out the new arena than the Awesome Brawlers!/The Ancient Elder: Dan finds a new baku-bud in Gillitar. Well "bud" may be too strong a word, Dan and gang quickly learn that Gillator has a few "quirks" that keep him from fitting in with the rest of the Awesome Brawler's Bakugan.

title: Craig and the Kid's Table
description: It's a Williams Family Thanksgiving, which means it's time to reunite The Kid's Table! But when Bernard accidentally destroys dessert, Craig uses the power of the Kids Table to help save his brother from certain grounding.

title: Working for Scales
description: Princess Zange is sick and requires a dinosaur scale for a tea remedy, but King Rexxtopher is fiercely against the Warriors stepping foot inside his Dinosaur Kingdom to get it.

title: Drawn to Expression
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American, Pacific Islander Heritage Month, and recognizing awesome kids all over the country who are drawn to, expression.

title: Drawn to Family
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American, Pacific Islander Heritage Month, and recognizing awesome kids all over the country who are drawn to, family.

title: The Haunted Dollhouse
description: Craig and his friends find themselves being followed by a creepy doll and its haunted dollhouse.

title: Conduciendo A La Locura
description: Cuando la Chatarra se rompe en un parque de casas rodantes, Ben descubre que se encuentran en la última etapa del Cali 10 Hundred-una carrera de autos épica todo terreno-en la que LaGrange, el piloto demente, ha regresado en busca de venganza contra aquellos que lo descalificaron hace años.

title: Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray
description: Dr. Animo has broken out of jail, and has been tracking down Ben, intent on revenge. At the same time, Ben's broken off a piece of the Omnitrix, and as a result, has turned into weird alien combinations, i.e. StinkArms.

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: Together Forever
description: Connie has a really clear vision for her future. Steven wants to make sure he'll be a part of it.

title: This Man, This Man Man!
description: When Guts Man goes on a ravenous rampage across the city, Mega Man must turn to an unlikely ally, Man Man, a bumbling DIY human analog to our hero.

title: Back to the Library
description: Uncle Grandpa uses time travel to convince his past self to return a library book on time.

title: E. Nigma, Consulting Detective
description: When the Joker traps Batman, the Justice League decides against their better judgment to allow Riddler, who is trying to go straight, to help them track him down.

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Villain Time
description: Ben must go alien to save the Hoover Dam from disaster, but when tough guy hero Tim Buktu swoops in to help, Ben must figure out if Tim is friend or foe.

title: Mushroom Menace
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman wants the Warriors For Hire to defend her giant pumpkin home from the dreaded Smashroom Mushroom, but Vambre and Prohyas can't complete their mission without help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword!

title: La Celula Nucleo
description: Los Fantásticos defienden la Célula Núcleo de un ataque de Tiko, y en el último intento de Dan por salvarla, él y Drago logran liberar un nuevo poder.

title: Gem Hunt
description: Steven and Connie track a Gem monster through the wilderness but its tracks lead them to mystery.

title: Plant Daddies
description: When Ms. Baker pairs up the kids to act as parents for a sprout, Sumo and Clarence learn all about good parenting. Jeff buys toys instead of fertilizer and Chelsea and Kimby get to know each other.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star Part 2
description: The competition heats up and Robin tries everything to win.

title: Monkey See, Doggie Do/Mommy Fearest
description: Monkey See, Doggie Do: Mojo unleashes a curse on Townsville that turns everyone into dogs, including the Powerpuff Girls! Luckily, they manage to sniff out a solution and show Mojo that their bite is worse than his bark./Mommy Fearest: When Professor Utonium falls for the lovely Ima Goodlady, the girls quickly discover that Ima's not such a good lady after all. She's really the sinister Sedusa!

title: Gamers Never Say Die
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to find a rare, golden video game patch.

title: Hot Sauce
description: A quest for their favorite hot sauce causes the Bears to get involved with a sting operation.

title: The Pest
description: When they find Anais training herself for a brutal showdown, Gumball and Darwin realize their sister is being pestered at school by an annoying kid, Billy. They try to teach her how to resolve the problem peacefully but Billy has other ideas.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Quien se llevo a Pan
description: Cuando Pan desaparece de la fiesta de Unikitty, ila princesa lidera una búsqueda para encontrarlo y desenmascarar al secuestrador de tostadas!

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Garage Door
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to fix the garage door.

title: Trick or Threat
description: Four kids in Justice League costumes are trick or treating on Halloween when they investigate a spooky house. As dangers befalls them inside, they come to realize that maybe they're not kids at all, but real Justice Leaguers under a spell.

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Suelta
description: Cuando el espíritu de Adorabat trasciende su cuerpo durante un ejercicio de meditación, Mao Mao y Colosal tienen que descubrir un modo de devolverla al mundo real.

title: Grown Up Stuff
description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

title: Dark Birth Part 1
description: While Starscream acquires new power through the Allspark, the Autobots mistakenly assume Starscream is still under Megatron's command.

title: The Petals
description: When Leslie's petals begin falling off he feels like his good looks are fading, Gumball and Darwin use everything they know about style and beauty to try and help him. The only problem is they know nothing about style or beauty. As Gumball and Darwin's methods become more extreme, Leslie questions whether he's prepared to make the ultimate sacrifice for beauty.

title: Problemas Dentales
description: A Puppycorn se le cae su primer diente, y Unikitty está emocionada por su hermanito, ique ahora recibirá la visita de la legendaria Hada de los Dientes! Pero cuando el Hada de los Dientes no aparece, Unikitty y sus amigos asumen la responsabilidad. ¿Acaso se meterán demasiado rápido y con demasiada soltura con los dientes sueltos y tocarán un nervio sensible?

title: El silencioso
description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Hora De Ser Villano
description: Ben debe transformarse en alienígena para evitar un desastre en la represa Hoover, pero cuando Tim Buktu, el heroico tipo rudo, se precipita para ayudar, Ben debe descubrir si Tim es su amigo...o su enemigo.

title: Dia de Spa
description: Los Osos se relajan en el spa. Grizz intenta usar todos los servicios del spa. Panda queda atrapado en la sala de vapor con un anciano. Y Polar juega al ping pong.

title: Thunderhowl Part 1
description: Bumblebee and Chromia travel to Crystal City to recover one of Windblade's psychic shards and encounter a long-lost bot.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Second Greatest Team Edition Part 1
description: The Justice League holds another talent competition to find the second best superhero team in the world.

title: El castigo de mi vida
description: Owen forma un nexo especial con Duncan después de que ambos se divirtieran mucho durante sus castigos.

title: El Cumpleanos de Panda
description: Para el cumpleaños de Panda, los Osos intentan ayudarlo a conocer a su banda favorita de K-pop, Monsta X.

title: The Bike Ride
description: Pizza Steve desperately tries to prevent the gang from finding out his shameful secret.

title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Hogar, dulce hogar
description: Los Fantásticos vuelven a casa y se dan cuenta de que el tiempo no ha pasado. Pronto descubren que su conocimiento acerca de las batallas ha aumentado de forma exponencial.

title: Elements Part 5: Slime Central
description: Finn and Jake infiltrate the new Slime Kingdom and are drawn into a heated skate battle.

title: Juego de mascaras
description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Saca tu Bestia
description: Craig quiere jugar a un popular juego de cartas, así que decide tomar prestadas las cartas antiguas y valiosas de Bernard.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: Carl
description: A pleasant weekend goes awry when a monster attacks.

title: El primo Jon
description: Cuando los Osos asisten a una reunión con la familia de Chloe, se convierten en víctimas de Jon, el travieso primo de Chloe.

title: Idolo De La Liga De La Justicia: Edicion Del Segundo Mejor Equipo
description: La Liga de la Justicia organiza un concurso de talentos para encontrar al segundo mejor equipo de superhéroes.

title: Panda's Birthday
description: For Panda's Birthday, the Bears try to help Panda meet his favorite K-Pop band, Monsta X.

title: Trials Part 2
description: Cheetor attempts to judge whether Optimus or Megatron are more worthy of the Allspark, but an unexpected visitor dashes all the bots' plans.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Tim Buk-TV
description: Team Tennyson heads to the Okefenokee Swamp to witness the blooming of the Blushing Orchid, something that happens once every one hundred years. But their plans get disrupted when Tim Buk-Tu, trying to make his new 'reality' show more exciting, endangers the rare flower and everyone else at the swamp.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: Hip hip Hurra
description: Bridgette tiene hipo y está desesperada por librarse de ellos.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: Fallen Arches/The Mane Event
description: Fallen Arches: When a gang of old-time villains come out of retirement, the girls enlist the best superhero team of the past to save the city./The Mane Event: Bubbles and Buttercup are playing with Blossom's beautiful locks when an accident happens. Now, Blossom is too embarrassed to put up a good fight.

title: Arrested Development
description: Ben and Rook must stop the evil Robots from Dimension 12 while trapped in their own pre-pubescent bodies, thanks to Ben's childhood rival.  (Introducing Billy Billions.)

title: Drive You Crazy
description: After the Rust Bucket breaks down at a Mobile Home Park, Ben discovers they've stumbled on to the last leg of the Cali 10 Hundred, an epic, off-road auto race where mad driver Le Grange has returned for revenge against those that disqualified him years ago.

title: Little Sword of Horrors
description: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late!

title: Frenemy
description: When the coolest girl in school befriends the girls, she charms them into becoming her accomplices in a series of adventurous crimes.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: The Picnic
description: Gumball and Darwin barely survive a school picnic in the Forest of Doom

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 1
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: Idolo De La Liga De La Justicia P2- Edicion Del Segundo Mejor Equipo
description: La competición se intensifica y los Titanes deben encontrar una forma de vencer a la Colmena.

title: OK A.U.!
description: An evil warlock takes our heroes to a strange alternate universe.

title: The Return of Party Horse
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to help their friend Party Horse get back together with his girlfriend.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val le guarda rencor a Vic, lo cual atrae sin querer a un malvado cadejo, una bestia mitológica parecida a un lobo.

title: Una ninja justicia para Harold
description: El mundo de Harold queda de cabeza cuando sus compañeros declaran que Beth es la verdadera ninja de la clase.

title: Phased and Confused
description: When members of the Justice League are affected by the Phantom Zone ray and become phantom-like, their only hope for freedom is to somehow get a message to Booster Gold.

title: Proximo Idolo de la Liga de la Justicia: Parte 1
description: La Liga de la Justicia organiza un concurso de talentos para encontrar a un superhéroe digno de unirse al equipo.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Show de momias
description: Duncan sale en una misión para espantar a Courtney durante una excursión al museo.

title: On Your Toes
description: After a Porcupunk sighting, Axel leads a recon mission that slowly but surely proves to be a wild goose chase devised by Sarge, who's secretly pursuing a hobby that he's afraid to share with his teammates.

title: The Last Donnycorn
description: When Donny the Unicorn is hunted by a seemingly unstoppable foe, the Powerpuff Girls have to find a way to save him before it's too late!

title: Hic Hic Hooray
description: Bridgette gets the hiccups and becomes desperate to get rid of them.

title: Digital Quality
description: Ben and Gwen don't want to go to the CD Library. CDs are for old people. Ew. Once Team Tennyson is there, Lord Decibel traps them inside and demands a ransom. Ben and Gwen find Kevin inside on a potentially nefarious quest of his own, but it turns out that Lord Decibel may have already found the item that they so desperately desire.

title: The Throw Down/Brawl for It All
description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Second Greatest Team Edition Part 2
description: The competition heats up and the Titans must find a way to beat the Hive Five.

title: El verdadero potencial
description: Justo cuando los ninjas piensan que han salvado el día, Lord Garmadon regresa a Ninjago, y libera a Harumi, quien lo anima a "alcanzar su verdadero potencial" conquistando lo único que siempre se interpuso en su camino, su hijo, Lloyd.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Splitsville
description: The girls learn to appreciate each others's style after having to each fight solo.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: Viral Spiral
description: When the Amoeba Boys wreak havoc on the internet, Bubbles has to hack her sisters in to stop them.

title: Insect Inside/Powerpuff Bluff
description: Insect Inside: Vile villain Roach Coach has a plan to infest Townsville with an army of cockroaches! The girls overcome their squirms to squash Roach Coach's scheme and force him to bug off./Powerpuff Bluff: Three local hoods get new identities when they find grown-up-sized Powerpuff costumes inside Townsville Jail. They terrorize Townsville while the Mayor mistakenly sends the real girls to the slammer.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Who Took Toast
description: When Toast disappears from Unikitty's party she leads a search to find him and expose the toast-napper.

title: Perro Decisivo
description: Incapaz de tomar decisiones difíciles, Craig decide poner sus decisiones en manos de un perro llamado Fred.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Una extrana conexion
description: Drago lidera a los Bakugan contra la amenaza de Tiko, para proteger una poderosa fuente de energía.

title: Watchtower Tours
description: When Booster Gold starts to secretly give tours of the Watchtower to make some extra cash, he inadvertently brings in a super villain disguised as a tourist.

title: Legend of Torbaclaun
description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

title: Hiccup Havok
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a kid who can't get rid of the hiccups.

title: Welcome to the Underworld 1
description: After Victor loses a wrestling match, Victor and Valentino journey to the underworld to seek advice from their uncle, a famous wrestler named El Toro.

title: The Quiet One
description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

title: The Photo
description: It's school picture day and Gumball has until 3pm to take one good photo - or have his legacy ruined forever.

title: Tomorrow Today
description: When Max drags the kids to see a defunct "House of the Future" built by his childhood idol, Ben discovers Steam Smythe is busy excavating the joint on the search for a powerful device that will allow him to create devastating weapons for his war on progress. Only Max's devotion to his childhood idol and Ben's faith in dreams can save tomorrow... today!

title: A Bot and His Dog
description: Tired of fielding of low stakes house calls, Mega Man gets what he wishes for when Hypno Woman hijacks the local power plant.

title: Just Friends
description: Rigby and Eileen get called away to Don's black belt ceremony forcing Mordecai and Margaret to hang out alone.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: Drawn to Food
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American, Pacific Islander Heritage Month, and recognizing awesome kids all over the country who are drawn to, food!

title: Yuri and the Bear
description: Baby Ice Bear lives alone in the arctic and meets a mysterious man named Yuri. Together they help each other survive the cold environment.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Future
description: Steven is finally ready to move on.

title: Villains' Night In
description: While Boxman and Venomous are out, Fink is reluctantly babysat by Darrell and Shannon.

title: Showdown Part I
description: The Faction infiltrates Galvan in an attempt to destroy Azmuth.  (Introducing new Nemetrix aliens Omnivoracious & Vicetopus.)

title: Fun Proof
description: Apple and Onion want to become this week's "Most Fun People".

title: Flirty Phantom
description: Lost in Transylberia, the Warriors come to a haunted house for help and meet a young ghost lady inside that wants to spend the rest of her afterlife with Prohyas!

title: Beach Episode
description: Surf's up on a wacky beach adventure when our heroes are challenged to the ultimate beach battle.

title: An Unlikely Ally
description: Lloyd runs afoul of the Ice Emperor's Blizzard Samurai but is rescued by a strange wolf with whom an unlikely friendship develops.

title: La Leyenda del Torbaclaun
description: Cuando los Corazoncitos creen que el mítico Torbaclaun ha llegado al Valle Puro Corazón, Mao Mao intenta demostrarles que no es real.

title: Furniture & Meat
description: Big money problems send Finn and Jake to Wildberry Kingdom.

title: Bakugan Wynton/The Boy from Brazil
description: Bakugan Wynton: Wynton has a new device that tracks down Bakugan! Right out of the gate the device works and, Wynton meets: Batrix. Like his name, Batrix is a little batty, and these two are certainly in for a "batty" first adventure./The Boy from Brazil: The Awesome Brawlers are off to a soccer match! In the process of doing so Shun discovers a new Bakugan friend, the boisterous Ramparian, and a new foe in Brazilian soccer star: Pepe.

title: Ben Again
description: When Eon causes 11-year old Ben swap minds with teen Ben, it's up to Gwen, Rook, and Professor Paradox to set things straight.  (Featuring Eon and Professor Paradox.)

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

title: Clarence Wendle and the Eye of Coogan
description: Clarence and other students find the crusty old journal of Coogan filled with clues leading to a mysterious treasure. Clarence spearheads the team of treasure hunters to journey through the perils of Aberdale seeking the lost Eye of Coogan.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Sneaky Peeky
description: After missing out on a chance to see the premiere of the new Robofrog movie trailer, the trio devises a plan to sneak into the theater and catch a glimpse before anyone else. However, when they accidentally damage the reel, they're forced to fix it or fess up!

title: The Tails of Mardrynia
description: After reading a book about a mystical animal society in class, Clarence is inspired to round up local animals and recreate an animal world of his own to cheer up his friend Percy. But will Percy take the game too far?

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: #TweenTitans
description: Jessica Cruz is hired by billionaire playboy Bruce Wayne to chaperone young Dick Grayson's Metropolis birthday bash and brings Karen Beecher along to help, but the girls get more than they bargained for when the TWEEN party guests reveal their TITANic personalities.

title: Sworn to the Sword
description: Connie trains with Pearl to be a swordfighter.

title: The Password
description: Gumball and Darwin are shocked to discover that Anais is Dad's favourite child. Mom has forced Dad to install a password on the computer. The pop-up clue advises them that the password is the name of Dad's favorite child. After trying "Gumball" and "Darwin" unsuccessfully, they discover the answer is, in fact, "Anais". They are determined to become Dad's favorites by any means necessary, even if it means undermining each other, plotting against Anais or driving a wedge between mom and dad . . .

title: A Ninjustice to Harold
description: Harold's world is turned upside down when Beth becomes the class ninja.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: Store 23
description: While out looking for the elusive 23rd Mr. Smoothy's store with Blukic and Driba, Ben meets an alternate version of himself. (Guest-starring Aziz Ansari as Ben 23.)

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Manana Es Hoy
description: Cuando Max arrastra a los niños a ver una "Casa del futuro" obsoleta construida por su ídolo de la infancia, Ben descubre que Vapor Smythe está ocupado excavando el lugar en busca de un dispositivo poderoso que le permitirá crear armas devastadoras para su guerra en progreso. Solo la devoción de Max por su ídolo de la infancia y la fe de Ben en los sueños puede salvar el mañana...ihoy mismo!

title: #EmperorPenguin
description: When Barbara Gordon attempts to do something nice for a friend, she ends up in the clutches of the Penguin, a high school mob boss who blackmails her into an increasingly desperate situation from which only Batgirl can save her.

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: T.G.I.S
description: The Secret Saturdays come to Bellwood to investigate a rash of chupacabra attacks.

title: Wild Wild Wheel Part 2
description: WildWheel finds Optimus Prime rebuilding a small Cybertronian town, only to discover the Prime does not recognize him.

title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 2
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: Uncle Melvins
description: Legendary rock band, the Melvins, team up with Uncle Grandpa to help a young girl who wants to win her school's talent show.

title: Tooth Trouble
description: Puppycorn loses his first tooth and Unikitty's excited for her little bro, now he​ ​gets a visit from​ ​the​ ​legendary Tooth Fairy!​ ​But when the Tooth Fairy is a no-show, Unikitty and her friends take on the mantle and responsibilities. But will they play too fast and loose with loose teeth and hit a raw nerve?

title: La Maldicion
description: Craig, Kelsey y JP entran en conflicto con unas brujas adolescentes deshonestas, ique les lanzan una maldición! iQué adolescentes malvadas!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: That's a Wrap
description: Duncan goes on a mission to scare Courtney during a field trip to the museum.

title: The Good Lars
description: Steven, Lars and Sadie get invited to a party with the Cool Kids.

title: Stop the Presses
description: Richard's newspapers aren't selling, so his friends pull out all the stops to put the printed word back on top.

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Thank You for Watching the Show
description: When KO finds moments of his life slipping by, he begins to suspect something weird is going on.

title: Harley Goes Ape!
description: When Gorilla Grodd takes control over Titano, the giant ape, the only person who seems to be able to override his control is the medical worker who nursed him as a chimp. She's now known as Harley Quinn.

title: Fallo de tigre
description: Gwen se niega a que la presionen para elegir un sabor de helado que no quiere.

title: Big Fat Alien Wedding
description: Ben and Gwen accompany Max to a wedding, which doesn't make Ben particularly happy, especially given the fact he has to wear a tux and learn how to dance. During the wedding it's revealed that the bride's parents are aliens while the groom's family are ex-Plumbers. It turns out the bride's parents are out to sabotage the wedding because of a long lasting feud with the Plumbers, and take action by demonstrating their destructive powers and causing deadly havoc. Ben, Max and Gwen enter the fray and not only save the day, but make sure the ceremony goes on as planned.

title: Dread on Arrival
description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

title: Thunderhowl Part 2
description: Released after eons of imprisonment, Thunderhowl helps Bee and Chromia navigate the dangerous Crystal City.

title: A Guilded Cage
description: Mega Man must stop Namagem and an army of hypnotized Good Guild bots from breaking into Dr. Light's lab.

title: Un Aliado Peculiar
description: Lloyd se enfrenta a los Samurais Blizzard del Emperador de Hielo, pero es rescatado por un lobo extraño con quien desarrolla una amistad peculiar.

title: Dark Birth Part 2
description: The Autobots and Decepticons battle aboard the Nemesis while Starscream uses the Allspark and Vector Sigma to create new allies.

title: Terror llegando
description: Los ninjas recurren al comisionado de la policía de Ninjago en un esfuerzo por ayudar a salvar a Lloyd y frustrar los esfuerzos de Harumi de resucitar al malvado Lord Garmadon.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Party Horse
description: The guys want to help Party Horse pass his U.S. history test.

title: Pruebas de Diversion
description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren convertirse en la "Gente más divertida" de esta semana.

title: Boogie Frights/Abracadaver
description: Boogie Frights: The Boogie Man creates perpetual night by launching a huge disco ball to block out the sun. While evil creatures are dancing and destroying in the dark, the Powerpuff Girls plot to crash the ball./Abracadaver: Al Lusion, the old-time Townsville magician, pulls off his greatest stunt yet when he comes back from the dead as the zombie Abracadaver to haunt Townsville.

title: Dr. Dometome
description: Lion-O is tasked with mapping the beaches of Third Earth, which leads to him somehow draining the oceans of all water entirely. Woops! But a mysterious scientist with a robotic frog says they can fix everything by traveling under the earth, which is just the kinda crazy adventure Lion-O is all about!

title: Mandora - The Evil Chaser
description: Lion-O "accidentally" releases a whole space prison-full of space criminals and winds up on the wrong side of the law. On the right side of the law is Mandora the Evil Chaser, a no nonsense space cop! Lion-O's gonna have to work real hard to prove he's not a criminal, just a little bit of an oaf!
